Human Genome Diversity Project + gnomAD callset with phased genotypes (n~4000 individuals)
https://gnomad.broadinstitute.org/downloads#v3-hgdp-1kg
Downloaded with gsutil:
gsutil -m cp -r gs://gcp-public-data--gnomad/resources/hgdp_1kg/phased_haplotypes .

And then rename

Renamed hgdp1kgp_chrX_non_par.full.shapeit5_rare.bcf
to
hgdp1kgp_{chr}.filtered.SNV_INDEL.phased.shapeit5.bcf
